name: Bright USA Map
description:
The Bright USA Map is a cheerful and educational map that would make a great addition to a kid's room or playroom. Inspire a love of learn and an appetite for adventure in your little one.

- The map is printed on a heavy weight 100% recycled paper with a matte finish, using archival inks. 
- 19" x 13" or 22" x 17"
- Ships rolled

name: Map of Montreal
description:
The Map of Montréal was originally created for Pure Green Magazine. The map accompanied a tour of the city as described by well-know Montréal blogger, Lake Jane. All of your favourite neighbourhoods can be found, from Westmount in the west to Hochelaga in the east, from Ville Marie in south to Jean Talon in the north. The city is bursting with things to do and places to see, and this print exudes Montréal's joie de vivre.

- The map is printed on a heavy weight 100% recycled paper with a matte finish, using archival inks. 
- paper dimensions: 19" x 13", artwork dimensions: 16" x 12"
- Ships rolled

name: Bright World Map
description:
The Bright World Map features the countries of the world in a rainbow of colours. The perfect piece to brighten up a child's bedroom, the World Map is both a fun piece of art as well as educational.

- The map is printed on a heavy weight 100% recycled paper with a matte finish, using archival inks. 
- 19" x 13" / 22" x 17"
- Ships rolled

name: Animal Alphabet Poster
description:
Designed to inspire young minds, the Animal Alphabet poster is a fun and colourful way to teach children both their ABC's and animals. It's the perfect addition to any bedroom or nursery, and makes a great gift for a new baby.

Professional digital print on 11 point silk, FSC-certified 30% recycled paper. The colours are vivid and the poster looks great framed in a standard 15.75" x 19.75" frame.

Dimensions: 13" x 19"

The poster is shipped in a durable mailing tube.

name: Custom Name Print - Small
description:
The one-of-a-kind Custom Name Print makes a unique and fun gift for a new little baby, or to decorate your child's nursery or room.

Using the letters of the child's name and corresponding animals, I will create a personalized 8" x 10" print for you. 

When ordering a Custom Name Print please provide me with the following information via a 'message to seller' at the check-out, or an email to: bess [at] englishmuffinshop [dot] com:

• The name you would like on the print
• Which 2 or 3 colours would you like for your print
• Any additional information, ie. colour of the nursery, etc...

The artwork is professionally printed on high quality FSC certified, satin-finish cover stock.

To see more examples of Custom Name Prints, please visit my Flickr page:
http://www.flickr.com/photos/englishmuffinshop/sets/72157625922689501/
